memberdef.argsstring: (ModelAnimation owner, String name, CmdGeneration cmdGen, boolean showInReport, boolean showInTrace, boolean showInAnimation)
memberdef.name: ModelAnimation

detaileddescription.para:
ModelAnimation extends Model about a CmdGeneration instance and a showInAnimation switch. In constructor you must define: setModelAuthor(..), setModelDate(), addRemark(), addIcon() and setGeneratedBy()
owner
supermodel, may be null
name
name of model
cmdGen
CmdGeneration object
showInReport
switch for report generation
showInTrace
switch for trace generation
showInAnimation
switch for cmds-file generation
place to init black-box components and there createAnimation Statements
overwrite presentTime from Model. Originally, before experiment start presentTime is 0. Now, in initPhase presentTime is initTime (from cmdGeneration object)
overwrites init from Model with: initCmds(), initEntityTypes(), and initAnimation()
generate "createModelBasisData" Command and EntityTypeAnimation Commands used by init()
check setting of modelAuthor, modelDate and remarks used by initCmds()
Animated version of model. ModelAnimation extends Model about a CmdGeneration instance and a showInAnimation switch. A animated model must extend form ModelAnimation.
